https://www.codewars.com/kata/57cebe1dc6fdc20c57000ac9

My resolution: 

def find_short(s):
    lista = s.split()
    lenght = int("inf")
    for world in lista:
        if (len(world) < lenght):
            lenght = len(world)

    return lenght


Other cleaver resolutions:

return min(len(x) for x in s.split())

return min(map(len, s.split(' ')))
